    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my car, and she\u2019s been absolutely wonderful to own. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes. I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with all the regular maintenance, so it\u2019s running smoothly and ready for many more adventures with a new owner! It\u2019s a great, dependable ride that still looks sharp in the driveway. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take a look\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
