      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained 2018 Executive Sedan that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and reliability. The exterior is finished in a stunning Deep Sea Blue Metallic that retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, though I\u2019ve noted a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the Oyster Dakota leather interior remains supple and clean; it has been a strictly smoke-free and pet-free environment. All onboard electronics, from the premium surround-sound system to the dual-zone climate control, function exactly as they should. Mechanically, this vehicle is in excellent health. I have kept a complete log of all scheduled maintenance, including a recent comprehensive service and brake pad replacement just 2,000 miles ago. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts are crisp and imperceptible. While there is very light wear on the driver\u2019s seat bolster, the overall cabin feels fresh and inviting. This is a dependable, well-cared-for vehicle ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
